{"tid":2178964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Lunch哥稱警爆粗：成班警署軍裝拍手","createTime":"2020-08-28T19:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:01:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"48515260310e7aeb16f9d9affd6d7de314580cbb","tid":2178964,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/FABOOWN5EZEUXNBPTMRMGT3KJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FFABOOWN5EZEUXNBPTMRMGT3KJY%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=4e29ed8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FFABOOWN5EZEUXNBPTMRMGT3KJY%2F&h=2e756bb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/FABOOWN5EZEUXNBPTMRMGT3KJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n稱「Lunch哥」的中六學生David周二被警方以涉嫌公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為罪被捕，經歷48小時的拘留後，周四被帶上法庭。他說相對早前的一次被捕及多次被截停搜查的經驗，這次被捕經歷是最差的一次。<br />\n<br />\n「點解差人舉中指就冇事」<br />\n「去到警署，係咁俾便衣警指住鬧！用粗口不斷鬧我！」辱罵David的是一位高級督察，15分鐘不停指罵，粗言穢語橫飛，David上庭後回到家，怒氣仍未消，說到那位辱罵自己的警察，他越說越激動，「佢鬧我，後面成班軍裝喺度食花生，係咁拍手叫好」。<br />\n<br />\n警員對着17歲的他說「等天收」、「玩得咁過癮，有排你受」，還有此起彼落的掌聲，David卻說自己不害怕，讓警員隨便說任意罵，因為他知道必須沉住氣，口舌之爭只會把自己放在不利的位置，「由得佢講，鬧咗一陣見我冇反應，佢哋自己收聲」。"},{"pid":"79e8a6d0088b96c6c873ba8562342f7d52df36fa","tid":2178964,"uid":79410,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:01:44.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家. 屌佢老母. <br />\n知唔知個黑警知乜名? 睇下屋企人有冇外國護照?"},{"pid":"bed275a89f68f790f1be0138bd3fd56313f1dce1","tid":2178964,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"狗吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雜耍"},{"pid":"be2bc10072d7bfb6839c2558341bafa3ecd11a68","tid":2178964,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:07:19.000Z","msg":"爛仔黎"},{"pid":"d6474d78a6c667639e47e24c2314b00aec6ff895","tid":2178964,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0